Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Riku Voipio <riku.voipio@linaro.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 12), pkg-config, dh-autoreconf, dh-exec (>= 0.3), zlib1g-dev, libacl1-dev, libcmocka-dev <!nocheck>, liblzo2-dev, uuid-dev, libzstd-dev
Build-Conflicts: libssl-dev
Standards-Version: 4.3.0
Homepage: http://www.linux-mtd.infradead.org/
